## 📌 Overview

This repository serves as my complete portfolio for the **AI in Medical Imaging Summer Series**. The course progresses from ML fundamentals to the cutting-edge architectures powering modern medical AI, including:

- **Classical ML**: SVMs, Scikit-Learn pipelines
- **Deep Learning**: Perceptrons, CNNs, Vision Transformers
- **Medical Imaging**: X-ray, MRI, CT, Ultrasound, Pathology
- **Medical Tasks**: Classification, Regression, Segmentation, Generation
- **Hands-on Models**: BioMedCLIP, RAD DINO, UNet, NVIDIA Generative Models

Each session includes hands-on code, real medical datasets, and clinical reasoning, culminating in a capstone project.

